e new culture with which they interact.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aWomen immigrantszIllinoiszChicago. 0aWomenzEurope, NorthernxSocial conditions. 4aU.S. History. 4aWomens Studies.1 aHarzig, Christiane, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Archive Pre-2000z978311053617140uhttps://doi.org/10.7591/978150172554840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501725548423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501725548/original  a978-3-11-053617-1  Cornell University Press Archive Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles